have a look at the code samples we've given

00:45:35.190 --> 00:45:36.190
here.

00:45:36.190 --> 00:45:38.789
And take a look at the new Jelly Bean APIs
for this and they'll be good to go.

00:45:38.789 --> 00:45:39.789
&gt;&gt; NI-LEWIS: Exactly.

00:45:39.789 --> 00:45:41.829
So, we've already shown how to handle full
screen correctly.

00:45:41.829 --> 00:45:45.880
If they take that to heart I think they'll
have a much better user experience.

00:45:45.880 --> 00:45:47.299
&gt;&gt; MEIER: Absolutely.

